Milestones Map React Native App
A React Native app to search, add, and display milestones on a map with route visualization. Uses LocationIQ API for place search and react-native-maps for map rendering.

Features
Search places with LocationIQ API (autocomplete).

Add selected places as milestones.

View milestones on an interactive map with markers.

Display route line connecting milestones.

Remove milestones with validation (minimum 3, maximum 10).

Debounced search to reduce API calls.

Clean and user-friendly UI.

