Run the app:

bash
Copy
Edit
npx expo start
or

bash
Copy
Edit
npm start
Usage
Use the search input to find places.

Tap on a search result to add it as a milestone.

View your milestones list below the search.

Remove milestones by tapping the "Remove" button.

See all milestones and route on the map.

Dependencies
React Native

Expo

react-native-maps

axios

Notes
The map centers on the first added milestone.

Maximum 10 milestones can be added.

Minimum 3 milestones must be present to allow removal.

Estimated duration per milestone is fixed at 30 minutes (customize as needed).

LocationIQ API is used for place search. Get your API key at https://locationiq.com.

